{
  "texts": [
    "Considering efficiency, reliability, and resource costs, we chose to utilize SSCI and SCI-indexed journals.",
    "The data analysis confirmed this decision's efficacy, identifying key issues.",
    "Yet, for future endeavors, we propose to develop a strategy to streamline screening within vast datasets from multiple databases, enhancing comprehensive results.",
    "Regarding methodology, we employed topic modeling-based bibliometric analysis, distinct from systematic analysis focusing on a limited number of articles based on predefined dimensions (e.g., the weakness, strengths, and challenges of each application of AI or datasets and achieved results on them).",
    "Topic modeling-based bibliometrics offer rapid, automatic large-scale data analysis, extracting crucial topics not confined to AI applications or datasets used."
  ]
}